  "rationale": "<p>Write both terms over the common denominator <i>m</i>: 36<i>b</i>/<i>m</i> + 36<i>b</i><i>m</i> = 36<i>b</i>/<i>m</i> + 36<i>b</i><i>m</i>&sup2;/<i>m</i> = (36<i>b</i> + 36<i>b</i><i>m</i>&sup2;)/<i>m</i> = 36<i>b</i>(1 + <i>m</i>&sup2;)/<i>m</i>. The other choices result from incorrectly combining the terms.</p>",
